== 剧情 ==
Cecil Gaines（角色原為[[尤金·艾倫|尤金·艾倫]]）是一位在[[白宫|白宫]]工作了34年（1952年至1986年）的非裔美国管家，他亲眼目睹了20世纪许多重大历史事件<ref>{{cite news |last=Child |first=Ben |title=The Butler trailer: Oprah Winfrey in the White House |url=http://www.guardian.co.uk/film/2013/may/09/the-butler-trailer-forest-whitaker |accessdate=10 May 2013 |newspaper=[[The_Guardian|The Guardian]] |location=London |date=9 May 2013 |archive-date=2013-07-16 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20130716100645/http://www.guardian.co.uk/film/2013/may/09/the-butler-trailer-forest-whitaker |dead-url=no }}</ref><ref>{{cite news |last=Roberts |first=Roxanne |title=Trailer for 'The Butler,' based on life of the White House's Eugene Allen |url=http://www.washingtonpost.com/blogs/reliable-source/wp/2013/05/08/trailer-for-the-butler-based-on-life-of-the-white-houses-eugene-allen/ |accessdate=10 May 2013 |newspaper=[[The_Washington_Post|The Washington Post]] |date=8 May 2013 |author2=Amy Argetsinger |archive-date=2014-11-29 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20141129083000/http://www.washingtonpost.com/blogs/reliable-source/wp/2013/05/08/trailer-for-the-butler-based-on-life-of-the-white-houses-eugene-allen/ |dead-url=no }}</ref>，主要展现了[[非裔美国人|黑人]][[民权运动|民权运动]]的斗争进步史。

